# Component Standards

- Keep UI components under `src/components/ui`.
- Components should be presentational and stateless unless interactivity is required.
- Use Astro props with typed interfaces and safe default values.
- Expose variants through explicit props (for example `variant="primary"`).
- Add ARIA attributes and labels for form and popup components.
- Keep one responsibility per component and avoid deeply nested component trees.
